	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just wanted to add that Flash of Light is probably one of the best taunts we paladins have, even at level 43 I use it consistantly to pull mobs off overambitious casters.&nbsp;&nbsp;Even when FoL is resisted, it almost always causes the mob to make a beeline for you.  The only thing you have to be careful of, of course, is staying near the mob within melee distance so it doesn't run off and pull some friends.  I still consider it one of my best spells and is ALWAYS memmed.<br><br>On a different subject, I play a HIE paladin, and my stamina is ungodly low (79 from 70 base) so my hp are decidedly lacking.  Can anyone recommend some sta items that won't compromise AC and are readily attainable to a 43?<br><br>Shaiserosia Dar'Temdrache<br>Torvonnilous<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
