	   <tr><td colspan=2>yes i agree that a monk with FD would be a better puller... hehe if your pulling vox your ac wouldnt matter much when you start running with her pounding on your back(woudn't get too far) but a monk with a shurikan and sow could easily pull her into a huge ambush and then FD until she is taunted away... also as for maintaning aggro... keeping the high lvl MOB on you for the whole fight would be a lot harder on your group healer! paired up with a ranger or sk or warrior you can hack at it and take the dmg evenly.(1 guy in front 1 in back and slash it up and when 1 guy is getting more dmg then the other then you taunt it off)<br><br>pallies ARE damage absorbers, but we arn't invincible :P&nbsp;&nbsp;we may be one of the next choices to a monk, but not better.<br>&nbsp;<br>-Omnislayer Darktide<br>-Omnislayerr Darktide<br>&lt;Erud's Chosen&gt;<br>Knights of TZ<br></td></tr>
